pan style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除非用戶特意表明，否則服務供應商不可自動替用戶續約。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來好多人唔知中移動一直違規，仲傻仔咗比違約金轉台<br />\n<br />\n追究到底，要求中移道歉加賠償(如未經同意自動續咗)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用中移就預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"Pish 中字無好"},{"pid":"a443e07ad1b3d4525cb4655c637e278ddf741473","tid":1354923,"uid":180576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"好耐收到信以前比佢罰500違約 打上去同佢講 <br />\n通訊局唔比未經授權自動續約 無權罰我<br />\n之後咁多年都無再收信"},{"pid":"310266bb2accf386775f7eca9431890d61327cd5","tid":1354923,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"452b106a48ab58f0923429cd460aed83434a118f","tid":1354923,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a610cd0ff27c363762d07f01a4c47659e15d1ddb","tid":1354923,"uid":131616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4d402530732a4285feaa34a0dc5de58cb0e39c","tid":1354923,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"只見到一定要簽名，無得揀唔到喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"以前(我舊number 15年前簽左舊合約)係揀到,而家揀唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"即係強制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁咪咗OFCA違規囉，唔怪得啲人一投訴，佢就免違約金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"唔簽嗰個位唔係代表唔同意？"},{"pid":"d980de3cd5792ea3be13588ce011c16ce779566a","tid":1354923,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"451334e1739304911791e6ded4c27db52aa4be59","tid":1354923,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be22bb186afa9091a8fc1e47a2b5c22f18ee3696","tid":1354923,"uid":131616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0